OL,3,CCompany fined after man run over by
OL,4,Ctruck on first day of work
OL,6,FA waste and recycling company has been
OL,7,Ffined after a man was run over on his
OL,8,Ffirst at work.
OL,10,FThe 40-year-old was hand picking waste
OL,11,Fwhen he was hit from behind by a
OL,12,Fmoving shovel loader. The digger drove
OL,13,Fover the man and had to reverse when
OL,14,Fthe alarm was raised by nearby
OL,15,Fcolleagues.
OL,17,FWheeldon Brothers Waste Limited have
OL,18,Fnow been fined #250,000 after an
OL,19,Finvestigation by the Health and Safety
OL,20,FExecutive.
