OL,3,CCompany fined after man run over by
OL,4,Ctruck on first day of work
OL,6,FAfterwards, the man spent one week in
OL,7,Fhospital because of his injuries. He's
OL,8,Freturned to working for a different
OL,9,Fcompany.
OL,11,FWheeldon Brothers Waste Limited, of
OL,12,FBury New Road, Bury, Lancashire,
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to breaching Section
OL,14,F2(1) of the Health and Safety at Work
OL,15,Fetc Act 1974, was fined #250,000 and
OL,16,Fordered to pay #4102.32 costs at a
OL,17,Fhearing at Manchester Magistrates'
OL,18,FCourt on April 2.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
