OL,6,FAfter the hearing, HSE principal
OL,7,Finspector Lisa Bailey said: "This man
OL,8,Fis lucky to be alive.
OL,10,F"Vehicles such as shovel loaders
OL,11,Frequire plenty of space due to the
OL,12,Fnumber of blind spots and poor
OL,13,Fvisibility.
