OL,3,CCompany fined after man run over by
OL,4,Ctruck on first day of work
OL,6,F"This incident was easily avoidable by
OL,7,Fimplementing control measures and safe
OL,8,Fpractises. Measures should have been
OL,9,Fimplemented to ensure that workers
OL,10,Fpresent in the yard were not put at
OL,11,Frisk from moving vehicles in and
OL,12,Faround where they were working,
OL,13,Fincluding rigorous pedestrian and
OL,14,Fvehicle segregation and safe refuge
OL,15,Ffor workers whilst vehicles are
OL,16,Foperating.
